revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yearbys}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yearby'' is the 23397<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 1087 individuals. ''Yearby'' is most common among Black/African American (76.26%) and White (18.49%) individuals.
